Package org.nineml.coffeegrinder.tokens

package org.nineml.coffeegrinder.tokens
The token classes.

Tokens are what the parser consumes. Often this is a sequence of characters, but it can also be a sequence of strings or, in fact, arbitrary items.

  • Classes
